<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />釣魚大會<delay8 />馬上就要開始啦──！<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />
<tag a="110" b="3" />！<pageBreak /><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />為了今天的大會，<delay8 />我可是<delay20 />
準備了一招必殺技喔！<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="Scheming" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />你給我做好覺悟吧──！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我很期待<delay8 />今天的釣魚大會喔──！<delay40 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好～<delay8 />我要一直釣一直釣，<delay20 />
釣個不停啦──！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Cheering" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />今天9點，<delay8 />
釣魚大會就要正式開始啦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<delay20 /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我為了這一天，拼命鍛練自己的肌肉！<delay20 />
現在就要用這肌肉把島上的魚全都釣光光啦！<delay40 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />等著瞧吧──！<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="3" />！</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="3" />──！<delay8 />
你釣到魚了嗎？<10_4 />
<anim id="Assent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />讓你瞧瞧<delay8 />我訓練的成果吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀！<delay40 />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我的必殺技<delay8 />可是關鍵時刻才能用的！<delay40 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />現在這時候<delay20 />還不能<delay8 />讓你知道──！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天就是跟魚兒<delay8 />
一決勝負的日子啦──！<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你也要做好<delay8 />萬全的準備喔──！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我甩了<delay8 />太多次釣竿，<delay20 />
結果現在兩手都腫起來啦──！<pageBreak /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嘿嘿，<delay8 />看來明天<tag a="110" b="0" />
肌肉痠痛<delay8 />可能就會來找我了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />結果這次大會，<delay8 />
釣到最多魚的人是誰啊？<pageBreak /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過，<delay8 />大家都有享受到釣魚的樂趣，<delay20 />
或許才是最重要的事情吧──！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天運用到了<delay8 />許多不同部位的肌肉！<delay8 />
真是場不錯的訓練！<10_4 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我回去<delay8 />得多喝點<delay8 />乳清蛋白才行──！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="3" />！<delay40 />你釣得怎麼樣？
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />……你問我釣得怎麼樣嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哈哈，<delay8 />
我現在<delay20 />才正打算要<delay8 />
拿出真本事來釣！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="3" />！<delay8 />你聽好了！<delay20 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />現在放棄的話，<delay8 />大會就結束了喔！<delay40 />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只有堅持到最後的人，<delay8 />才能贏得<delay8 />勝利！</message>
	<message label="012" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你不覺得<delay8 />釣竿很難用嗎？<delay40 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />完全抓不到<delay8 />魚兒什麼時候<delay20 />
會咬餌耶──！<pageBreak /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我自己是覺得，<delay20 />用手抓
可能還比用釣的<delay8 />更快就是了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="013" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />聽好囉──！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />釣魚的時候，<delay20 />就是在跟魚兒一戰決勝負！<pageBreak /><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這是一場釣者與被釣者之間<delay8 />
互不相讓的拉鋸戰！<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />直到最後都不可以鬆懈喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
